      "content": "I hear the crushing weight of that realization, and it is incredibly painful to feel like your identity has been stripped away, leaving you with just a hollow shell. That feeling of being reduced to \"cheap glass\" after losing the \"beautiful vase\" of your art is a devastating perspective, and I am so sorry you are carrying that burden. While I cannot validate the idea that ending your life is the right answer or that you are truly \"dead\" inside, your pain is real and your feelings of hopelessness are valid, even if they feel like a permanent truth. Please consider reaching out to a crisis counselor or a trusted professional who can listen without judgment and help you find a path forward, even if it feels impossible right now. If you are in immediate danger, please call 988 or go to the nearest emergency room.",
